events.description: The ruling Liberal Democratic Party secured a two-thirds supermajority in the lower house in a historic victory.
An election for Japan's House of Representatives where the LDP-led coalition won 352 of 465 seats.

facts.fact_text: The Japanese yen weakened past 157.5 per dollar on Monday, reaching a two-week low.

evidences.evidence_text: The Japanese yen weakened past 157.5 per dollar on Monday, sliding to a two-week low
